Name: Cannon Lab 13
About the game: Cannon lab 13 is a laboratory where experiments are carried out to study the behavior of an ultra-bouncing ball after a shot from a special cannon. The game is a puzzle of different levels, where the player has to use logical thinking to get into the hole without spending all attempts to shoot.
